            <Paragraph Margin="10,20,0,0" Tag="SA15numberone">
                <Run Text="1." FontWeight="ExtraBold" FontSize="30"></Run>
                The developer shall utilize a software/firmware development process that explicitly addresses software/firmware security requirements; implements secure coding standards; identifies the tools used in the development process; documents the specific tool options and configuration used in the development process; documents, manages, and ensures the integrity of changes to the process used for development.
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph TextAlignment="Left" Margin="50,20,0,0">
                <Run Text="Maps To:"  FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="15" ></Run>
                <Run Text="CCI-003233, CCI-003234, CCI-003235, CCI-003236, CCI-003237, CCI-003238, CCI-003239, CCI-003240"  FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="15" ></Run>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="70,20,0,0">
                The organization requires the developer of the information system, system component, or information system service to follow a documented development process.
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="50,20,0,0">
                <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                <Run Text="Implementation Guidance" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="30" />
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="70,20,0,0">
